Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「花映难波津 隆冬且暂隐」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.69,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なにわずに　さくやこのはな　ふゆごもり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「初春又将至 再绽此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:10.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的节目看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看了看了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生里边有模特绫濑千岁的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 我是她的粉丝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是超可爱的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 我们去看看吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个班?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过听说每天午休时都在休息厅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑…千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}かるた（歌留多，骨牌）：用有画的牌来进行的一种竞技游戏，\N竞技歌留多使用小仓百人一首进行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竞技歌留多部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 四 !
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那是什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动服?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 那腰带怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又穿成那种样子…这么不注重仪表!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是您说这种时候不能穿裙子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要穿运动服 就全身从上到下都只穿运动服!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你那传单也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要贴的话只能贴一张
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在这里脱!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:31.94,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你口口声声说要搞竞技歌留多部 上古文课却又一直在睡觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 别人说她虽然有张难得的漂亮脸蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要一活动一开口 形象就全毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人称「白搭美女」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:53.02,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(559,213)\blur11\fad(984,1013)}再绽此花矣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「歌留多」什么的就放弃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是一起玩田径吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短跑都进市比赛了 太可惜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多是…「祸福皆因强出头」那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}原文是「犬も歩けば棒にあたる」，\N出现在古典版的竞技歌留多中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说田径部应该叫「邂逅系」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邂逅系?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该去参加活动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然前辈又要生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见啦 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那个前辈啊 可真够恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊… 有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来都决心一定要在高中找到同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百投入歌留多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 绫濑就是女王了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}女王（クイーン），指在全国歌留多比赛中，授予\N参加女性组比赛并获得日本第一名的人的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:05.55,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「谁为我知己 未语可知心…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:05.55,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}たれをかも　しるひとにせむ　たかさごの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正觉得玩歌留多很快乐 是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你总这样「大」字躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会被人说成是「白搭美女」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:17.36,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「高砂松虽寿 不及故人情」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:17.36,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}まつもむかしの　ともならなくに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一居然在同一个高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你一定直升进名校的高中部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单程要一个半小时才能到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要接着读3年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说刚才那下很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是千早你考上都立的好高中 让我很意外…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们根本没差多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会再长的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也还会再长…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一太一太一 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你不怎么受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在? 在车站啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 你在分倍河原车站等吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 有女朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点受打击了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被告白了我才和她交往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那么的喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新也找到了比歌留多更重要的事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和新…有联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年连贺年卡也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…好像去年也没参加全国大会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学在田径部 也没参加过近江神宫的全国大会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}最高级别的全国大会基本都在近江神宫举行，\N因此也被称为竞技歌留多的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加田径部 不也很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 高中会做些其他事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多终究只是兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 太一不玩歌留多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得在同一所高中的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中学也是以足球部为主的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能永远玩歌留多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「谁为我知己 未语可知心」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:09.36,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たれをかも　しるひとにせむ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首和歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说以前的朋友都已经不在了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续玩下去的话就能再见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要再见面啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前 在东京
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我 还未曾找到热衷的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 你姐姐的选美比赛如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然闯进了最后一轮…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 明天的报纸会刊登姐姐的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的姐姐很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太一也这么想?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和千早不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你就只有运动能赶得上我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有身高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 想打架吗 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个转校生根本不说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和那家伙扯上关系比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说那家伙把虫当零食吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班有人看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袜子上还有洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班不需要他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把绵谷的福井方言记下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最近他都不说话了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有新东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很小气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 那次啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是绵谷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会跟为了嘲笑他而记笔记的人说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也…不是想那么做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗? 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你忘记拿路线表啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说记住了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天才刚开始做啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可有200多家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别送错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2丁目5区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原先生和他对面的5家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大泽 藤宫 山本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内山先生退订了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横田公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,101 103 203 204
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一家 绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐上报纸了哦 快醒醒!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 还有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正还是落选了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能入选最后15人也很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把这个照片给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:11:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这个得大奖的人身材确实更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别总这么说话不经大脑啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 我看新闻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 好厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厉害 真的登了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 明明是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早却还是像个男孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}百人一首：收集一百位歌人各一首的和歌集，\N一般指最出名的「小仓百人一首」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位 百人一首的贴纸集齐没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百首都记住了的话 就来参加测试哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.46,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不可能的啦 你记住多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.30,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}才记住10首 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住的人就可以参加下个月的歌留多比赛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:39.88,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}15个~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.22,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}这也没差多少吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你记住多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多才到一半吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了行了 学习比不过你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真岛同学 你已经完全记住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是什么都做得来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不只是真岛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班还有一个人 也记住了全部一百首哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.45,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天放学以后 绵谷同学来参加测试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气背出了一百首哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.04,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好厉害~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真的是一口气背下来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月的歌留多大会 你也会出场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…会的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送报纸的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷同学早上送报纸了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然送报纸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学生是不允许打工的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…绵谷同学 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有叫我帮忙的时候…才去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为家里太穷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 他一直都穿同一条裤子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷同学很了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能送报纸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家安静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也要加油把一百首都背下来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见咯 真岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 把你唯一的行头弄湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要穿的衣服没了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆问妈妈借裙子穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到你会做这么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你干嘛总是帮他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要这样 说不定明天起也会被孤立的哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会不管你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说真的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候你就算哭我也不管!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好破啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个人就是说话不经大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上也是因为这个挨了姐姐一脚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…可以说话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会记笔记的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么早上…要等报纸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐参加了选美大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早点看到那个报导
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的这个人就是我姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吧 厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想 就是有一天姐姐能成为日本第一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种是不能称之为梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自己的事情 就不算是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以把梦想寄托在别人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你姐姐就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绵谷同学有什么梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于你自己的!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这不就是百人一首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说会不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校每年都会举办歌留多大会的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 今天老师不也说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我…我们来比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以 但是没有人来读啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有磁带啊 磁带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…怎么弄来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把25张牌分成三段排好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到上句读出来 就要拿掉下句对应的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}上句（上の句），指短歌的前半五·七·五三句，\N下句（下の句）则指剩下的第四、第五句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在才只背下来50个左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只是个歌留多比赛而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种眼神 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋来红叶散…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.59,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あらしふく…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天工织做锦 还缀龙田川」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:29.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,662)}たつたのかはの　にしきなりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又扎到门里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今时辛酸泪 老来润心田」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:42.83,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ながらへば　またこのごろや　しのばれむ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:54.46,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「世间千般愁 欲解竟无方」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:54.46,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}よのなかよ　みちこそなけれ　おもひいる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多…以前是这样玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要抢到一张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张牌的上句我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「激流戏浅水 岩前两纷飞」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.58,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,658)}せをはやみ　いはにせかるる　たきがはの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要抢到那一张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有那一张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要抢到!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.68,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「激…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.68,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:51.81,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「…流戏浅水 岩前两纷飞」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:51.81,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}…をはやみ　いはにせかるる　たきがはの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从绵谷同学那里抢到一张了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算什么啊 强得过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是绫瀬同学也抢到了一张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这一张啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我很开心!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在福井的时候 经常和朋友们一起玩歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 东京却没什么人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是一个人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人? 听着磁带?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多在其他国家都没什么人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为确实比较难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这也就意味着…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本取得第一的话 就是世界第一了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…第一?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加歌留多比赛 成为名人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}名人：与女王相对，是授予男性的\N代表歌留多日本第一名称号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千早」…是个好名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这是属于你的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张牌的上句 是以「神代有蓬莱」开头的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.73,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,658)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为听到「ちはや」就要抢这张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.82,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,660)}千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}ちはやぶる，日文汉字可以写成「千早振」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这张牌就是「ちはや」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.78,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,660)}千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的眼中就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 这是你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 女朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小女朋友 吃地瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神代有蓬莱 今看龙田川」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:50.10,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちはやぶる　かみよもきかず　たつたがは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙真的好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇景未曾见 江揽红叶衫」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.70,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,からくれなゐに　みづくくるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次和新玩歌留多的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所知道的不是歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是新的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:22:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
